For such interaction to be successful, it is standardly thought that participant
s must be able to efficiently recursively model the mental states of others.
 The Canteen Dilemma is an online experiment intended at testing the extend
 to which people actually employ such higher order social cognition.
 The experiment therefore aims at finding out what difference there is between
 idealised models of social reasoning and the actual reasoning that humans
 employ.
